          "description": "Heals all non-burning allies for 500% of the user's Attack and grants them Sleep Thorns. When an ally with Sleep Thorns is dealt damage by an attack, that ally's Sleep Thorns will be consumed to immediately grant the Cursed Sleep status effect to the attacker. Burn or attacks that grant Burn will remove Sleep Thorns and prevent Cursed Sleep from applying. Usable if there are no Sleep Thorns on allies and the user is not burning.\n\nCursed Sleep will overwrite status effects other than Burn, cannot be overwritten by Poison, can be applied repeatedly to units that have already slept while on the battlefield, and will not end from damage caused by Dream Hunter type active skills.",
